  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You are adept at ripping away an opponent's mental mask, exposing its true visage during a psychic duel.</em><br /><br /><strong>Prerequisites</strong><br />Psychic Sensitivity or ability to cast psychic spells or use psychic spell-like abilities, character level 2nd.<br /><br /><strong>Benefits</strong><br />While in a psychic duel, when you create an offensive manifestation that can be negated or halved only with a successful Will saving throw, if your opponent fails that Will saving throw, its mental mask is shattered, revealing the opponent's true form.<br /><br /><strong>Special</strong><br />If you possess the Third Eye feat, your opponent&rsquo;s mental mask is shattered even on a successful Will saving throw.</p>",
